---
---
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-wrap">
      <div class="about-left reveal">
        <div class="clients-label">About Us</div>
        <h2>We're Not an Agency.<br>We're Your Creative 
          <span class="weapon-trigger">
            <span class="weapon-text">Weapon.</span>
            <svg class="ak47-svg" viewBox="0 0 120 40">
              <rect x="5" y="15" width="25" height="12" fill="currentColor" rx="2" />
              <rect x="30" y="14" width="45" height="10" fill="currentColor" />
              <rect x="75" y="16" width="35" height="4" fill="currentColor" />
              <rect x="110" y="13" width="2" height="7" fill="currentColor" />
              <path d="M45,24 L55,38 L68,38 L60,24 Z" fill="currentColor" />
              <rect x="38" y="24" width="10" height="14" fill="currentColor" rx="2" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </h2>
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>Founded with a vision for the future, Polaroid Dosa was built to solve a single problem: generic branding. We don't do "safe" and we don't do "average".</p>
          <br>
          <p>We partner with founders and brands that want to dominate their category through visual excellence and cinematic storytelling.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div class="stat-item"><h4>20+</h4><p>Films Produced</p></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><h4>30+</h4><p>Brands Worked With</p></div>
          <div class="stat-item"><h4>3x</h4><p>Avg. Client Growth</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-right reveal">
        <div class="about-card">
          <div class="about-card-ghost">PD</div>
          <div class="floating-badge">Available — for new projects</div>
          <div class="about-quote">"If it doesn't stop the scroll, it didn't earn a place on the screen."</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
